        "action": "Government to urge Israel to withdraw from Lebanon ",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We call on the UK Government to urge Israel to withdraw from Lebanon, stop occupying Palestinian land, and respect the rights of Lebanese and Palestinians.  We believe this would ensure justice, peace, and recognition of their biblical heritage.",
